				<li><a href="">New</a></li>
				<li><a href="">Popular</a></li>
				<li><a href="">Trending</a></li>
				<li><a href="">Categories</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</main>
	<main class="mainGrid">
		<section class="midSection">
			<img src={Game} alt="" width="100%" />

			<div class="midTitle">
				<h1>The Bright Future of Web 3.0</h1>
				<p>
					We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to
					put the power of the platforms back into the hands of the
					people. But is it really fulfilling its promise?
					<br />
					<button>READ MORE</button>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="rightSection">
			<div>
				<h2>New</h2>
				<h4>Hydrogen VS Electric Cars</h4>
				<p>Will hydrogen-fueled cars ever catch up to EVs?</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4>The Downsides of AI Artistry</h4>
				<p>
					What are the possible adverse effects of on-demand AI image
					generation?
				</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4>Is VC Funding Drying Up?</h4>
				<p>
					Private funding by VC firms is down 50% YOY. We take a look
					at what that means.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="bottomSection">
			<div class="1">
				<img src={PC} alt="" />
				<div>
					<h2>01</h2>
					<h3>Reviving Retro PCs</h3>
					<p>What happens when old PCs are given modern upgrades?</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="2">
				<img src={Laptop} alt="" />
				<div>
					<h2>02</h2>
					<h3>Top 10 Laptops of 2022</h3>
					<p>Our best picks for various needs and budgets.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="bottomSection">
			<div class="3">
				<img src={Controller} alt="" />
				<div>
					<h2>03</h2>
					<h3>The Growth of Gaming</h3>
					<p>How the pandemic has sparked fresh opportunities.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style lang="sass">
	:root
		--softOrange: hsl(35, 77%, 62%)
		--softRed: hsl(5, 85%, 63%)
		--offWhite: hsl(36, 100%, 99%)
		--grayBlue: hsl(233, 8%, 79%)
		--darkBlue: hsl(236, 13%, 42%)
		--veryBlue: hsl(240, 100%, 5%)
		--size: 15px
		--family: "Libre Franklin", sans-serif

	*,
	*::after,
	*::before
		margin: 0
		padding: 0
		box-sizing: border-box

	main
		margin: auto
		padding: 1.5rem
		max-width: 80%

		h1
			font-size: 4rem
			line-height: 4rem
			font-weight: 800
			margin: 0

			svg
				float: left

		ul
			display: flex
			justify-content: space-between
			list-style: none
			float: right
			li
				padding-inline: 5rem 0
			a
				text-decoration: none
				color: inherit
	.mainGrid
		display: grid
		grid-template-columns: 1fr .5fr
		column-gap: 2rem
		row-gap: 2rem
		.midSection
			.midTitle
				display: grid
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr
				margin-top: 1rem
				p
					font-size: 16.5px
					line-height: 2rem
					button
						background: var(--softRed)
						outline: none
						border: none
						color: var(--offWhite)
						padding: 1rem
						margin: 1rem 0 0
						width: 11rem
						font-family: var(--family)
						font-weight: 700
						letter-spacing: 4px
		.rightSection
			margin-left: auto
			background-color: var(--veryBlue)
			color: var(--offWhite)
		.bottomSection

			display: grid
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr)
</style>
